: Think about wonders of creation, not Allah\u2019s essence","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 14, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, passed by some people who were thinking about the essence of Allah. The Prophet said, \u201cReflect upon acts of creation, but do not reflect upon the essence of the Creator. Verily, you cannot possibly measure Him.\u201d Source: al-'Az\u0323amah li-Abi\u0304\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":12142,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/02\/12\/blessings-all-anbiya-rusul\/","url_meta":{"origin":24428,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Salawat: Send blessings upon all the Prophets","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 12, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cSend blessings upon the Prophets and Messengers of Allah. Verily, Allah has sent them just as he has sent me.\u201d Source: Shu\u2019ab al-Ima\u0304n 119 Grade:\u00a0Hasan (fair) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":29335,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/05\/13\/let-allah-see-traces-blessings\/","url_meta":{"origin":24428,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Wealth: Let Allah see the traces of His blessings on you","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 13, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Malik ibn Nadlah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIf Allah has given you wealth, let the traces of his blessings and generosity be seen upon you.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 4063 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u0646 \u0645\u0627\u0644\u0643 \u0628\u0646 \u0646\u0636\u0644\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u062c\u0634\u0645\u064a \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38908,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/02\/27\/wala-wa-bara-awthaq\/","url_meta":{"origin":24428,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Loyalty: Firmest faith is alliance and disavowal for Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 27, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, the firmest handle of faith is loyalty for the sake of Allah, enmity for the sake of Allah, love for the sake of Allah, and hatred for the sake of Allah.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Kabi\u0304r lil-T\u0323abara\u0304ni\u0304\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":40190,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/05\/19\/spread-salaam-of-allah\/","url_meta":{"origin":24428,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Salaam: Spread peace of Allah on the earth","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 19, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, peace is one of the names of Allah Exalted that He has placed upon the earth, so spread peace between yourselves.\u201d Source: al-Adab al-Mufrad lil-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 989 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":18564,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/03\/17\/call-upon-allah-with-yaqin\/","url_meta":{"origin":24428,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Conviction: Call upon Allah with certainty, without distraction","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 17, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cCall upon Allah with certainty that He will answer you. Know that Allah will not answer the supplication of an unmindful and distracted heart.\" Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 3479 Grade: Hasan\u00a0(fair) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627